(1) There shall be exempted from the payment of levy under this Act— (a) the President; (b) representatives of foreign countries and of international organisations and such members of their staff as the Minister may approve; (c) officers, warrant officers and other ranks of the naval, military and air forces of Her Britannic Majesty, based in the United Kingdom while serving in Zambia; (d) any person on a temporary visit to Zambia.
