(4) A person exempted wholly or partially from the payment of levy under the provisions of this section shall be granted a certificate of exemption in the prescribed form: Provided that— (a) in the case of any person mentioned in subsection (1); or (b) in the case of a member of a class of persons exempted under the provisions of subsection (3); it shall not be necessary to grant a certificate of exemption . [As amended by Acts No. 23 and No. 48 of 1964, 22 of 1981 and 9 of 1992]
