(2) A register maintained under sub-section (1) shall contain the following details in respect of each leviable person : (a) his full name; (b) his residential and postal address; (c) the amount of levy due and payable by him each year; (d) a reference to receipts issued for levy paid; (e) the name and address of his employer. [As amended by Act No. 23 of 1964 ]
